Interface Module

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Module>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Modules>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<ModuleKey>

    public interface Module
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Modules>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Module>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<ModuleKey>

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module config
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/config.yang): 

     list module {
     key "type" 
 "name"
     leaf name {
         type string;
     }
     leaf type {
         type identityref;
     }
     choice configuration {
     }
     choice state {
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is config/modules/module

    To create instances of this class use ModuleBuilder.
